Company Overview of H Partners Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
H Partners Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It invests in the alternate markets. The firm employs a fundamental analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach while making its investments. H Partners Management, LLC was founded in December 2004 and is based in New York City.


