 H PARTNERS MANAGEMENT Overview



												   H Partners Management Llc is a hedge fund that manages 1.5 BN dollars in regulatory AUM and has 13 employees, of which 8 perform investment advisory functions. The manager's has disclosed holdings from 12/31/07 to 03/31/17. The fund's latest filing disclosed 1BN in positions, representing 78% of the manager's regulatory AUM.
												



